roversy with insinuations about her sexual identity.\", \"from\": 495, \"to\": 686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to theIOC, there is no indication that Khelif, who has fought in the women's circuit for years, including theTokyoOlympics, identifies as anything other than a woman.\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 864, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her father showed identity documents and her birth certificate to AFP, speaking from a rural village about 10 km from Tiaret, a city 300 km fromAlgiers.\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 1017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 931, \"end\": 934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9989377621244311, \"rank\": 0.000681926981023031, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}, {\"begin\": 983, \"end\": 989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tiaret\", \"score\": 0.9999995138728126, \"rank\": 4.861274780319148e-07, \"text\": \"Tiaret\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tiaret\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tiaret\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My daughter is a girl,\\\" said Omar Khelif.\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1060, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1048, \"end\": 1052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omar_Little\", \"score\": 0.9990683065110904, \"rank\": 0.0009216772688264725, \"text\": \"Omar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omar_Little\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omar_Little\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She was raised as a girl.\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is a strong girl; I raised her to work and be brave.\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1144, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She won against the Italian simply because she was stronger, and the other was weaker.\\\"\", \"fro